  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/db6eb5aae01f3186.jpg?v=1782531503\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>1. We think Jack's pretty darn cute &amp; if you do too, <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1iVAqFM\">please vote for him in this contest</a> for a local store called The Pump Station. It just takes a second and we would so appreciate it!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/161b44968695765b.jpg?v=1782531506\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>2. It's Black Friday online at Studio Calico. Grab some really great products at amazing prices. For those who missed out on this exclusive embroidery stencil kit, you can grab it now for just $2.99. Sale ends Saturday 12AM EST.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f25d1e827ce22977.png?v=1782531508\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>3. I am absolutely crazy about this (new to me) Instagram account, <a href=\"http://instagram.com/mommasgonecity#\">mommasgonecity</a>. I mean, is there anything better than puppies and babies together?! I think not.</p><p>4. I've been saying the serenity prayer on a daily basis (sometimes multiple times a day). \"God grant me the serenity to accept the things I cannot change; the courage to change the things I can; and the wisdom to know the difference.\" Also I've been trying to remember to pause and take deep breaths. Just did it now, and you should try it too. ;)</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/679366aa28cbbf7e.jpg?v=1782531511\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>5. Silhouette is having a HUGE holiday sale! Visit <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/black\">Silhouette</a> and enter the code TANGERINE for these amazing offers valid through December 8.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
